This application is a web based program for archiving certificate of veterinary inspections. Business case is to keep track of cattle movements between the States and being able to track a cattle shipment in case of an emergency outbreak. 

. generated model and initial CRUD screens using scaffold
. revised viewer templates to use form select and short date
. generated migration scripts
. incorporated the relationship “has-many” and “belongs to” within model and database schema
. executed unit test to: use “ymal” based setup data; validate required data fields at model level; walk thru one-to-many relationship among the models; 
. tracked and version control the dev iterations

